articles.title: Scarlett Johansson Takes Legal Action Against AI App Misusing Her Likeness - IGN
articles.description: Scarlett Johansson has taken legal action against an AI app and its parent company for illegally using her name and likeness for their advertisements. The ad has now been seemingly scrubbed from the internet.
